OL,5, HSBC has been fined #57.4m by the Bank 
OL,6, of England for "serious failings" over 
OL,7, its measures to protect customer       
OL,8, deposits.                              
OL,10,FThe bank failed to accurately identify 
OL,11,Fdeposits eligible for Britain's        
OL,12,FFinancial Services Compensation Scheme,
OL,13,Fthe Bank's Prudential Regulation       
OL,14,FAuthority (PRA) said.                  
OL,16,FUnder the scheme, customer deposits are
OL,17,Fprotected up to the value of #85,000.  
OL,19,FHSBC said it was pleased to have       
OL,20,Fresolved the "historic matter".        
